name: Cryptobox
body: CryptoBox is an AES based Encryption/Decryption app that utilizes 128-Bit AES for file encryption and decryption. Currenly all file formats are supported, but there's no support for folders/directories. CryptoBox utilizes PBKDF2 with SHA-1 with a million iterations to generate the AES key from the user password.
